data.description: Newer construction (2021) with an open floorplan conducive to entertaining and family time. Kitchen includes island, double sink, and lots of cabinets; Granite in kitchen and baths; LVP flooring in the living areas and tile in the baths; large closets; oversized laundry area; covered front and back porch; nice corner lot and convenient to everything (1 hour to Nashville, close to Bowling Green & Gallatin). Spacious full cedar fenced yard; safe location (nice for walks); city grocery store includes local farm fresh produce.
